<h3>Introduction</h3>

<p>This library is still in it&apos;s infancy and only supports very few types
of noise yet.</p>

<p>It offers both heavily optimized (tested only on SBCL so far) and
reference implementations if they are available.</p>

<h3>License</h3>

<p>This project is released under the simplified
<a href="http://www.opensource.net/licenses/bsd-license.php" >BSD</a> license.</p>

<h3>Features</h3>

<ul>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Perlin_noise" >Perlin noise</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simplex_noise" >Simplex noise</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voronoi" >Voronoi noise</a></li>
</ul>

<h3>Documentation</h3>

<p>None.  See the examples/textures.lisp.</p>

